liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: The Israeli army is awaiting a "political decision" on the timing of a major ground offensive on the Gaza Strip, according to a military spokesperson. Military spokesmen Lieutenant Richard Hecht and Daniel Hagari have told separate briefing today "a political decision" will set off any action against Hamas. "We will be holding discussions with our political leadership," Lt Hecht told one briefing. AFP
